config MODULE_sleep
  tristate "Sleep support (NOT FULLY IMPLEMENTED)"
  default m
  ---help---
    This is a module that handles all the stuff that happens when you aren't
    doing anything. Its main purpose in life is to put the iPod to sleep, but
    it doesn't do that yet; it does, however, switch to "Now Playing" if music
    is playing. Enable this--it'll get more useful later.
